title: NFL Pantheon Players
itunes:title: NFL Pantheon Players
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Colleen Wolfe – discuss the latest NFL news including the Rams' quarterback battle and if Cam Newton has already peaked as an NFL player. Then the heroes discuss the all-time best players in the NBA and NFL before wrapping the podcast by sharing some “Now What?” scenarios for certain NFL teams.
